(159, 12, 'JavaScript is one', 'JavaScript es uno', 'JavaScript is one of the most popular programming languages today.\r\nIt was created to make websites more interactive and dynamic.\r\nAt first, it only worked in web browsers for small tasks.\r\nNow, it also works on servers using platforms like Node.js.\r\n\r\nWith JavaScript, websites can react to what users do.\r\nYou can click a button and see results right away.\r\nThere is no need to reload the entire web page.\r\nThis makes websites feel faster and more comfortable to use.\r\n\r\nJavaScript is an interpreted language that runs without compilation.\r\nThis makes it easier for beginners to test and learn.\r\nYou can write code and see the result immediately.\r\nThat helps you understand what each part of the code does.\r\n\r\nThe language supports many programming styles and methods.\r\nYou can write object-oriented code or use functional programming.\r\nIt also works well with event-based programming like clicking events.\r\nThis flexibility is one reason it is used almost everywhere.\r\n\r\nYou can use JavaScript in mobile and desktop applications.\r\nIt is not just for websites, but for many platforms.\r\nThat makes it a great skill to learn today.\r\n\r\nJavaScript also includes many built-in objects and functions.\r\nYou can work with text, numbers, and even dates easily.\r\nOne of its strengths is working with the DOM.\r\nThe DOM is the structure of a webpage in the browser.\r\n\r\nWith JavaScript, you can change a webpage in real time.\r\nYou can add text, remove images, or update styles instantly.\r\nThis allows you to build full and interactive user interfaces.\r\n\r\nIt also handles asynchronous actions like loading data from a server.\r\nJavaScript uses promises, callbacks, and async functions for this.\r\nThat means it can wait for results without stopping everything.\r\n\r\nWhen learning JavaScript, it may seem difficult at first.\r\nThe syntax is different if you have never coded before.\r\nBut with practice and small projects, it gets much easier.\r\nEvery time you write code, you understand more about the logic.\r\n\r\nJavaScript works closely with HTML and CSS on web pages.\r\nTogether, they form the base of any modern website.\r\nYou can change text, move elements, or apply animations.\r\nAll that is possible thanks to the power of JavaScript.\r\n\r\nIn conclusion, JavaScript is more than a basic scripting language.\r\nIt is a powerful tool for building modern digital experiences.\r\nIf you keep practicing, you will improve both code and English.\r\nYour thinking will become clearer and more logical every day.', '[{\"content\":\"JavaScript is one of the most popular programming languages today.\",\"translation\":\"JavaScript es uno de los lenguajes de programaci\\u00f3n m\\u00e1s populares en la actualidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:08:45\"},{\"content\":\"JavaScript is one of the most popular programming languages today.\",\"translation\":\"JavaScript es uno de los lenguajes de programaci\\u00f3n m\\u00e1s populares en la actualidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:08:47\"},{\"content\":\"It was created to make websites more interactive and dynamic.\",\"translation\":\"Fue creado para hacer que los sitios web sean m\\u00e1s interactivos y din\\u00e1micos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:08:52\"},{\"content\":\"At first, it only worked in web browsers for small tasks.\",\"translation\":\"Al principio, solo funcion\\u00f3 en navegadores web para peque\\u00f1as tareas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:08:57\"},{\"content\":\"Now, it also works on servers using platforms like Node.js.\",\"translation\":\"Ahora, tambi\\u00e9n funciona en servidores utilizando plataformas como Node.js.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:09:04\"},{\"content\":\"JavaScript is one of the most popular programming languages today.\",\"translation\":\"JavaScript es uno de los lenguajes de programaci\\u00f3n m\\u00e1s populares en la actualidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:10:49\"},{\"content\":\"JavaScript is one of the most popular programming languages today.\",\"translation\":\"JavaScript es uno de los lenguajes de programaci\\u00f3n m\\u00e1s populares en la actualidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:10:51\"},{\"content\":\"It was created to make websites more interactive and dynamic.\",\"translation\":\"Fue creado para hacer que los sitios web sean m\\u00e1s interactivos y din\\u00e1micos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:10:56\"},{\"content\":\"At first, it only worked in web browsers for small tasks.\",\"translation\":\"Al principio, solo funcion\\u00f3 en navegadores web para peque\\u00f1as tareas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:11:01\"},{\"content\":\"Now, it also works on servers using platforms like Node.js.\",\"translation\":\"Ahora, tambi\\u00e9n funciona en servidores utilizando plataformas como Node.js.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:11:08\"},{\"content\":\"Now, it also works on servers using platforms like Node.js.\",\"translation\":\"Ahora, tambi\\u00e9n funciona en servidores utilizando plataformas como Node.js.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:15:34\"},{\"content\":\"With JavaScript, websites can react to what users do.\",\"translation\":\"Con JavaScript, los sitios web pueden reaccionar a lo que hacen los usuarios.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:15:42\"},{\"content\":\"You can click a button and see results right away.\",\"translation\":\"Puede hacer clic en un bot\\u00f3n y ver los resultados de inmediato.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:15:48\"},{\"content\":\"There is no need to reload the entire web page.\",\"translation\":\"No hay necesidad de recargar toda la p\\u00e1gina web.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:15:52\"},{\"content\":\"There is no need to reload the entire web page.\",\"translation\":\"No hay necesidad de recargar toda la p\\u00e1gina web.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-08 23:15:58\"},{\"content\":\"This makes websites feel faster and more comfortable to use.\",\"translation\":\"Esto hace que los s