ctions\",\"translation\":\"Funciones de JavaScript\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:37:27\"},{\"content\":\"Functions are reusable blocks of code that perform a task\",\"translation\":\"Las funciones son bloques de c\\u00f3digo reutilizables que realizan una tarea\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:37:32\"},{\"content\":\"Function declaration example\",\"translation\":\"Ejemplo de declaraci\\u00f3n de funci\\u00f3n\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:37:43\"},{\"content\":\"function greet name returns Hello followed by the name\",\"translation\":\"La funci\\u00f3n greet name devuelve Hello seguido del nombre\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:37:50\"},{\"content\":\"Arrow functions\",\"translation\":\"Funciones de flecha\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:37:53\"},{\"content\":\"Arrow functions are a shorter syntax for writing functions\",\"translation\":\"Las funciones en flecha son una sintaxis m\\u00e1s corta para escribir funciones\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:37:58\"},{\"content\":\"Example of arrow function that adds two numbers\",\"translation\":\"Ejemplo de funci\\u00f3n de flecha que suma dos n\\u00fameros\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:38:13\"},{\"content\":\"const add equals open parenthesis a comma b close parenthesis arrow a plus b\",\"translation\":\"const add equals par\\u00e9ntesis abierto a coma b par\\u00e9ntesis cerrado flecha a m\\u00e1s b\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:38:22\"},{\"content\":\"If the function has only one parameter you can omit the parentheses\",\"translation\":\"Si la funci\\u00f3n s\\u00f3lo tiene un par\\u00e1metro, puede omitir los par\\u00e9ntesis\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:38:39\"},{\"content\":\"Example\",\"translation\":\"Ejemplo\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:38:51\"},{\"content\":\"const square equals x arrow x times x\",\"translation\":\"const cuadrado es igual a x flecha x veces x\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-08 03:38:55\"},{\"content\":\"JavaScript Variables\",\"translation\":\"JavaScript Variables\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-0