(163, 12, 'The Mysterious Letter', 'La carta misteriosa', 'The Mysterious Letter\r\nYesterday morning, I found a strange envelope on my small wooden desk, but I didn’t open it immediately.\r\nShe told me she had never seen it before, although her curious eyes followed my hands while I touched it.\r\nInside, there was an old photograph of two young boys holding their father’s large, weathered hat under the sunlight.\r\nI remembered my grandfather once mentioning a secret he had kept hidden in a box beneath his bed.\r\nWithout thinking, I placed the letter in my coat pocket and walked quickly toward the quiet park near our street.\r\nWhile I was sitting on the cold bench, a tall man approached me, asking politely if I was Mr. Collins.\r\nI said I wasn’t, yet I noticed he still looked at me as if he knew my family’s history.\r\nHe explained that his brother had written the letter twenty years ago, but it was lost during a stormy night.\r\nI asked him why it had appeared on my desk, and he simply smiled, pointing at the photograph in my hand.\r\nSuddenly, I realized the younger boy in the picture was wearing my father’s silver watch, the one he always carried.\r\nHe told me I should keep the letter safe, because one day it might help me find something I had been missing.\r\nBefore I could reply, he turned around, disappeared into the misty street, and left me holding a mystery in my pocket.\r\nI walked home slowly, wondering if my life had just changed, or if it was simply another strange morning in my quiet town.', '[{\"content\":\"The Mysterious Letter\",\"translation\":\"La misteriosa carta\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-10 13:23:58\"},{\"content\":\"The Mysterious Letter\",\"translation\":\"La misteriosa carta\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-08-10 13:24:00\"},{\"content\":\"Yesterday morning, I found a strange envelope on my small wooden desk, but I didn\\u2019t open it immediately.\",\"translation\":\"Ayer por la ma\\u00f1ana, encontr\\u00e9 un sobre extra\\u00f1o en mi peque\\u