(175, 22, 'In summary PHP', NULL, 'PHP is a popular language used to build dynamic and interactive web applications.\r\nOne important feature is the use of variables that always start with a dollar sign.\r\nWhen naming fields in HTML forms the names do not include the dollar sign.\r\nThis makes it easy to connect HTML input with PHP variables in the server.\r\n\r\nForms can send information using the method GET or the method POST.\r\nGET places the values inside the URL and the user can see them.\r\nPOST sends the values inside the body of the request and keeps them hidden.\r\nBoth methods allow PHP to receive information through the arrays GET and POST.\r\n\r\nTo redirect the user to another page PHP uses the HEADER instruction.\r\nHEADER with the option Location will move the user to a different address.\r\nAfter using HEADER developers usually write EXIT to stop the script execution.\r\nThis makes sure that no more code runs after the redirection is sent.\r\n\r\nIn HTML forms each field includes a TYPE attribute that defines its behavior.\r\nThe TYPE can be text number password email and many other different values.\r\nThe TYPE hidden is very useful because it hides the value from the user.\r\nIn PHP this hidden value is received exactly like any other normal value.\r\n\r\nA basic function in PHP is ECHO which prints results directly on the page.\r\nECHO can display strings numbers variables or even HTML fragments when needed.\r\nAnother option is PRINT which works in a similar way with small differences.\r\nFor debugging developers often use VAR DUMP to show variable contents.\r\n\r\nThere are many useful string functions like STRLEN and SUBSTR in PHP.\r\nSTRLEN returns the length of a string provided by the user input.\r\nSUBSTR can extract a specific part of a longer string for validation.\r\nThese functions are very helpful for controlling and processing user data.\r\n\r\nPHP also works with arrays including associative arrays with key and value.\r\nAssociative arrays let developers store and retrieve related information easily.\r\nThis structure is widely used in web applications for organization and clarity.\r\n\r\nIn summary PHP combines simplicity and power with many functions written in English.\r\nLearning names like GET POST HEADER TYPE HIDDEN or ECHO builds understanding faster.\r\nWith constant practice these words become natural and easy to remember forever.', '[{\"content\":\"PHP is a popular language used to build dynamic and interactive web applications.\",\"translation\":\"PHP es un lenguaje muy utilizado para crear aplicaciones web din\\u00e1micas e interactivas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:06:23\"},{\"content\":\"One important feature is the use of variables that always start with a dollar sign.\",\"translation\":\"Una caracter\\u00edstica importante es el uso de variables que siempre empiezan por el signo de d\\u00f3lar.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:10:52\"},{\"content\":\"When naming fields in HTML forms the names do not include the dollar sign.\",\"translation\":\"Cuando se nombran campos en formularios HTML los nombres no incluyen el signo de d\\u00f3lar.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:11:08\"},{\"content\":\"This makes it easy to connect HTML input with PHP variables in the server.\",\"translation\":\"Esto facilita la conexi\\u00f3n de entradas HTML con variables PHP en el servidor.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:11:24\"},{\"content\":\"Forms can send information using the method GET or the method POST.\",\"translation\":\"Los formularios pueden enviar informaci\\u00f3n utilizando el m\\u00e9todo GET o el m\\u00e9todo POST.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:11:41\"},{\"content\":\"GET places the values inside the URL and the user can see them.\",\"translation\":\"GET coloca los valores dentro de la URL y el usuario puede verlos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:12:00\"},{\"content\":\"POST sends the values inside the body of the request and keeps them hidden.\",\"translation\":\"POST env\\u00eda los valores dentro del cuerpo de la petici\\u00f3n y los mantiene ocultos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:12:14\"},{\"content\":\"Both methods allow PHP to receive information through the arrays GET and POST.\",\"translation\":\"Ambos m\\u00e9todos permiten a PHP recibir informaci\\u00f3n a trav\\u00e9s de las matrices GET y POST.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:12:38\"},{\"content\":\"To redirect the user to another page PHP uses the HEADER instruction.\",\"translation\":\"Para redirigir al usuario a otra p\\u00e1gina PHP utiliza la instrucci\\u00f3n HEADER.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:12:54\"},{\"content\":\"HEADER with the option Location will move the user to a different address.\",\"translation\":\"HEADER con la opci\\u00f3n Location mover\\u00e1 al usuario a una direcci\\u00f3n diferente.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:13:10\"},{\"content\":\"After using HEADER developers usually write EXIT to stop the script execution.\",\"translation\":\"Despu\\u00e9s de usar HEADER los desarrolladores suelen escribir EXIT para detener la ejecuci\\u00f3n del script.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:13:26\"},{\"content\":\"This makes sure that no more code runs after the redirection is sent.\",\"translation\":\"Esto asegura que no se ejecute m\\u00e1s c\\u00f3digo despu\\u00e9s de enviar la redirecci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:13:42\"},{\"content\":\"In HTML forms each field includes a TYPE attribute that defines its behavior.\",\"translation\":\"En los formularios HTML cada campo incluye un atributo TYPE que define su comportamiento.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:13:55\"},{\"content\":\"The TYPE can be text number password email and many other different values.\",\"translation\":\"El TIPO puede ser texto n\\u00famero contrase\\u00f1a correo electr\\u00f3nico y muchos otros valores diferentes.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:14:17\"},{\"content\":\"The TYPE hidden is very useful because it hides the value from the user.\",\"translation\":\"El TYPE hidden es muy \\u00fatil porque oculta el valor al usuario.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:14:36\"},{\"content\":\"In PHP this hidden value is received exactly like any other normal value.\",\"translation\":\"En PHP este valor oculto se recibe exactamente igual que cualquier otro valor normal.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:14:56\"},{\"content\":\"A basic function in PHP is ECHO which prints results directly on the page.\",\"translation\":\"Una funci\\u00f3n b\\u00e1sica en PHP es ECHO que imprime los resultados directamente en la p\\u00e1gina.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:15:11\"},{\"content\":\"ECHO can display strings numbers variables or even HTML fragments when needed.\",\"translation\":\"ECHO puede mostrar cadenas de n\\u00fameros variables o incluso fragmentos HTML cuando sea necesario.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:15:30\"},{\"content\":\"Another option is PRINT which works in a similar way with small differences.\",\"translation\":\"Otra opci\\u00f3n es PRINT, que funciona de forma similar con peque\\u00f1as diferencias.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:15:55\"},{\"content\":\"For debugging developers often use VAR DUMP to show variable contents.\",\"translation\":\"Para depurar, los desarrolladores suelen utilizar VAR DUMP para mostrar el contenido de las variables.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:16:10\"},{\"content\":\"There are many useful string functions like STRLEN and SUBSTR in PHP.\",\"translation\":\"Hay muchas funciones de cadena \\u00fatiles como STRLEN y SUBSTR en PHP.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:16:28\"},{\"content\":\"STRLEN returns the length of a string provided by the user input.\",\"translation\":\"STRLEN devuelve la longitud de una cadena proporcionada por la entrada del usuario.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:16:47\"},{\"content\":\"SUBSTR can extract a specific part of a longer string for validation.\",\"translation\":\"SUBSTR puede extraer una parte espec\\u00edfica de una cadena m\\u00e1s larga para su validaci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:17:02\"},{\"content\":\"These functions are very helpful for controlling and processing user data.\",\"translation\":\"Estas funciones son muy \\u00fatiles para controlar y procesar los datos de los usuarios.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:17:22\"},{\"content\":\"PHP also works with arrays including associative arrays with key and value.\",\"translation\":\"PHP tambi\\u00e9n trabaja con arrays incluyendo arrays asociativos con clave y valor.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:17:35\"},{\"content\":\"Associative arrays let developers store and retrieve related information easily.\",\"translation\":\"Las matrices asociativas permiten a los desarrolladores almacenar y recuperar f\\u00e1cilmente informaci\\u00f3n relacionada.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:17:53\"},{\"content\":\"This structure is widely used in web applications for organization and clarity.\",\"translation\":\"Esta estructura se utiliza mucho en las aplicaciones web por motivos de organizaci\\u00f3n y claridad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:18:12\"},{\"content\":\"In summary PHP combines simplicity and power with many functions written in English.\",\"translation\":\"En resumen, PHP combina sencillez y potencia con muchas funciones escritas en ingl\\u00e9s.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:18:35\"},{\"content\":\"Learning names like GET POST HEADER TYPE HIDDEN or ECHO builds understanding faster.\",\"translation\":\"Aprender nombres como GET POST HEADER TYPE HIDDEN o ECHO ayuda a comprender m\\u00e1s r\\u00e1pido.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:18:55\"},{\"content\":\"With constant practice these words become natural and easy to remember forever.\",\"translation\":\"Con la pr\\u00e1ctica constante, estas palabras se vuelven naturales y f\\u00e1ciles de recordar para siempre.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-16 10:19:12\"},{\"content\":\"PHP is a popular language used to build dynamic and interactive web applications.\",\"translation\":\"PHP es un lenguaje muy utilizado para crear aplicaciones web din\\u00e1micas e interactivas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-09-17 05:00:13\"},{\"content\":\"PHP is a popular language used to build dynamic and interactive web applications.\",\"translation\":\"PHP es un lenguaje muy utilizado para crear aplicaciones web din\\u00e1micas e interactivas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-11-07 12:40:16\"},{\"content\":\"PHP is a popular language used to build dynamic and interactive web applications.\",\"translation\":\"PHP es un lenguaje popular utilizado para crear aplicaciones web din\\u00e1micas e interactivas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 07:00:47\"}]', 1, 18, '2025-09-16 12:06:08'),
