 you do not fill in the title, it will be automatically generated with the first 3 words of the text.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-11-03 16:41:27\"},{\"content\":\"Si no llenas el t\\u00edtulo, se generar\\u00e1 autom\\u00e1ticamente con las primeras 3 palabras del texto\",\"translation\":\"If you do not fill in the title, it will be automatically generated with the first 3 words of the text.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-11-05 03:41:46\"}]', 0, NULL, '2025-11-03 20:33:36'),
(177, 23, 'Technology shapes modern', 'La tecnología da forma a la modernidad', 'Technology shapes modern life in ways people barely notice every single day.\r\nDesign and development require creativity, logic, patience, and constant learning from experience.\r\nStudents improve skills faster when they practice real projects with clear goals.\r\nGood interfaces feel simple, intuitive, and comfortable for all kinds of users.\r\nLearning programming can feel difficult, but progress appears with daily discipline.\r\nWeb development combines visual design with structured and efficient code logic.\r\nMultiplatform projects demand flexibility, testing, and attention to different environments.\r\nMistakes are normal and often teach more than immediate success ever could.\r\nTeamwork improves results when communication remains honest, direct, and respectful.\r\nModern tools evolve quickly, forcing developers to adapt without fear or hesitation.\r\nCreativity grows stronger when technical limits challenge original ideas and solutions.\r\nClear objectives help students stay focused and motivated during long learning processes.\r\nDesign decisions should always consider accessibility, usability, and performance equally.\r\nPractice builds confidence and transforms confusion into solid professional knowledge.\r\nEvery small improvement contributes to long term personal and professional growth.', '[{\"content\":\"Technology shapes modern life in ways people barely notice every single day.\",\"translation\":\"La tecnolog\\u00eda da forma a la vida moderna de maneras que la gente apenas percibe cada d\\u00eda.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:40:24\"},{\"content\":\"Design and development require creativity, logic, patience, and constant learning from experience.\",\"translation\":\"El dise\\u00f1o y el desarrollo requieren creatividad, l\\u00f3gica, paciencia y un aprendizaje constante a partir de la experiencia.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:40:48\"},{\"content\":\"Students improve skills faster when they practice real projects with clear goals.\",\"translation\":\"Los estudiantes mejoran sus habilidades m\\u00e1s r\\u00e1pidamente cuando practican proyectos reales con objetivos claros.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:01\"},{\"content\":\"Good interfaces feel simple, intuitive, and comfortable for all kinds of users.\",\"translation\":\"Las buenas interfaces son sencillas, intuitivas y c\\u00f3modas para todo tipo de usuarios.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:07\"},{\"content\":\"Learning programming can feel difficult, but progress appears with daily discipline.\",\"translation\":\"Aprender a programar puede parecer dif\\u00edcil, pero los progresos aparecen con la disciplina diaria.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:15\"},{\"content\":\"Web development combines visual design with structured and efficient code logic.\",\"translation\":\"El desarrollo web combina el dise\\u00f1o visual con una l\\u00f3gica de c\\u00f3digo estructurada y eficaz.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:20\"},{\"content\":\"Multiplatform projects demand flexibility, testing, and attention to different environments.\",\"translation\":\"Los proyectos multiplataforma exigen flexibilidad, pruebas y atenci\\u00f3n a los distintos entornos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:26\"},{\"content\":\"Mistakes are normal and often teach more than immediate success ever could.\",\"translation\":\"Los errores son normales y a menudo ense\\u00f1an m\\u00e1s que el \\u00e9xito inmediato.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:33\"},{\"content\":\"Teamwork improves results when communication remains honest, direct, and respectful.\",\"translation\":\"El trabajo en equipo mejora los resultados cuando la comunicaci\\u00f3n sigue siendo honesta, directa y respetuosa.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:34\"},{\"content\":\"Modern tools evolve quickly, forcing developers to adapt without fear or hesitation.\",\"translation\":\"Las herramientas modernas evolucionan con rapidez, lo que obliga a los desarrolladores a adaptarse sin miedo ni vacilaci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:41:41\"},{\"content\":\"Creativity grows stronger when technical limits challenge original ideas and solutions.\",\"translation\":\"La creatividad se fortalece cuando los l\\u00edmites t\\u00e9cnicos desaf\\u00edan las ideas y soluciones originales.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:42:37\"},{\"content\":\"Clear objectives help students stay focused and motivated during long learning processes.\",\"translation\":\"Unos objetivos claros ayudan a los alumnos a mantenerse centrados y motivados durante largos procesos de aprendizaje.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:42:48\"},{\"content\":\"Design decisions should always consider accessibility, usability, and performance equally.\",\"translation\":\"Las decisiones de dise\\u00f1o deben tener siempre en cuenta por igual la accesibilidad, la usabilidad y el rendimiento.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:42:54\"},{\"content\":\"Practice builds confidence and transforms confusion into solid professional knowledge.\",\"translation\":\"La pr\\u00e1ctica genera confianza y transforma la confusi\\u00f3n en s\\u00f3lidos conocimientos profesionales.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:43:01\"},{\"content\":\"Every small improvement contributes to long term personal and professional growth.\",\"translation\":\"Cada peque\\u00f1a mejora contribuye al crecimiento personal y profesional a largo plazo.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 13:43:07\"}]', 1, 21, '2025-12-17 12:40:17'),
(178, 23, 'Modern technology transforms', 'La tecnología moderna transforma', 'Modern technology transforms society by connecting people, automating tasks, and accelerating innovation across nearly every industry today.\r\n\r\nDigital platforms enable global collaboration, allowing individuals and companies to share knowledge instantly without geographic limitations.\r\n\r\nArtificial intelligence improves decision making by analyzing massive datasets, detecting patterns, and supporting faster, smarter solutions.\r\n\r\nCloud computing provides flexible infrastructure, reducing costs while increasing scalability, security, and accessibility for modern applications.\r\n\r\nMobile devices integrate powerful hardware and software, enabling constant communication, productivity, and entertainment in everyday life.\r\n\r\nCybersecurity becomes increasingly critical as digital systems expand, requiring advanced protection strategies against evolving online threats.\r\n\r\nEmerging technologies like blockchain and virtual reality redefine trust, ownership, and immersive experiences in digital environments.\r\n\r\nSustainable technology development focuses on energy efficiency, ethical design, and reducing environmental impact through innovation.\r\n\r\nUltimately, technology shapes the future of work, education, and society by continuously changing how humans interact.', '[{\"content\":\"Modern technology transforms society by connecting people, automating tasks, and accelerating innovation across nearly every industry today.\",\"translation\":\"La tecnolog\\u00eda moderna transforma la sociedad conectando a las personas, automatizando tareas y acelerando la innovaci\\u00f3n en casi todos los sectores.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:15:37\"},{\"content\":\"Digital platforms enable global collaboration, allowing individuals and companies to share knowledge instantly without geographic limitations.\",\"translation\":\"Las plataformas digitales posibilitan la colaboraci\\u00f3n global, permitiendo a particulares y empresas compartir conocimientos al instante sin limitaciones geogr\\u00e1ficas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:15:48\"},{\"content\":\"Artificial intelligence improves decision making by analyzing massive datasets, detecting patterns, and supporting faster, smarter solutions.\",\"translation\":\"La inteligencia artificial mejora la toma de decisiones analizando conjuntos de datos masivos, detectando patrones y apoyando soluciones m\\u00e1s r\\u00e1pidas e inteligentes.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:16:12\"},{\"content\":\"Cloud computing provides flexible infrastructure, reducing costs while increasing scalability, security, and accessibility for modern applications.\",\"translation\":\"La computaci\\u00f3n en nube proporciona una infraestructura flexible que reduce los costes al tiempo que aumenta la escalabilidad, la seguridad y la accesibilidad de las aplicaciones modernas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:16:23\"},{\"content\":\"Mobile devices integrate powerful hardware and software, enabling constant communication, productivity, and entertainment in everyday life.\",\"translation\":\"Los dispositivos m\\u00f3viles integran un hardware y un software potentes que permiten una comunicaci\\u00f3n, productividad y entretenimiento constantes en la vida cotidiana.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:16:39\"},{\"content\":\"Cybersecurity becomes increasingly critical as digital systems expand, requiring advanced protection strategies against evolving online threats.\",\"translation\":\"La ciberseguridad es cada vez m\\u00e1s cr\\u00edtica a medida que se ampl\\u00edan los sistemas digitales, lo que exige estrategias avanzadas de protecci\\u00f3n contra las amenazas en l\\u00ednea en constante evoluci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:16:54\"},{\"content\":\"Emerging technologies like blockchain and virtual reality redefine trust, ownership, and immersive experiences in digital environments.\",\"translation\":\"Tecnolog\\u00edas emergentes como la cadena de bloques y la realidad virtual redefinen la confianza, la propiedad y las experiencias inmersivas en entornos digitales.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-17 20:17:04\"},{\"content\":\"Modern technology transforms society by connecting people, automating tasks, and accelerating innovation across nearly every industry today.\",\"translation\":\"La tecnolog\\u00eda moderna transforma la sociedad conectando a las personas, automatizando tareas y acelerando la innovaci\\u00f3n en casi todos los sectores.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 15:41:20\"},{\"content\":\"Sustainable technology development focuses on energy efficiency, ethical design, and reducing environmental impact through innovation.\",\"translation\":\"El desarrollo de tecnolog\\u00edas sostenibles se centra en la eficiencia energ\\u00e9tica, el dise\\u00f1o \\u00e9tico y la reducci\\u00f3n del impacto ambiental a trav\\u00e9s de la innovaci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 15:43:16\"},{\"content\":\"Ultimately, technology shapes the future of work, education, and society by continuously changing how humans interact.\",\"translation\":\"En \\u00faltima instancia, la tecnolog\\u00eda configura el futuro del trabajo, la educaci\\u00f3n y la sociedad cambiando continuamente la forma en que interact\\u00faan los seres humanos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 15:43:26\"}]', 1, 18, '2025-12-17 19:15:24'),
(179, 23, 'Political ethics guides', 'Guías de ética política', 'Political ethics guides power toward justice and responsibility.\r\nLeaders must serve people, not personal ambition.\r\nMoral governance requires honesty, transparency, and respect.\r\nLaws should protect dignity and fundamental human rights.\r\nPower without ethics becomes oppression and corruption.\r\nEthical politics balances freedom, equality, and social responsibility.\r\nPublic decisions must prioritize common good over profit.\r\nAccountability strengthens trust between citizens and institutions.\r\nDialogue and tolerance prevent violence and polarization.\r\nJustice demands fair processes and equal opportunities.\r\nEthical leaders accept limits, criticism, and legal control.\r\nPolitical participation requires informed, critical, and active citizens.\r\nEthics reminds politics of its human purpose.\r\nWithout ethics, democracy weakens and public trust collapses.\r\nEthical politics seeks peace, inclusion, and sustainable development.\r\nEducation strengthens ethical judgment within political communities.\r\nMedia responsibility supports truth and democratic accountability.\r\nEthical compromise differs from betrayal of core principles.\r\nSolidarity connects individual interests with collective wellbeing.\r\nPolitical ethics evolves through culture, history, and reflection.', '[{\"content\":\"Political ethics guides power toward justice and responsibility.\",\"translation\":\"La \\u00e9tica pol\\u00edtica orienta el poder hacia la justicia y la responsabilidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:06:44\"},{\"content\":\"Leaders must serve people, not personal ambition.\",\"translation\":\"Los l\\u00edderes deben servir a las personas, no a la ambici\\u00f3n personal.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:06:50\"},{\"content\":\"Moral governance requires honesty, transparency, and respect.\",\"translation\":\"La gobernanza moral exige honradez, transparencia y respeto.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:06:54\"},{\"content\":\"Laws should protect dignity and fundamental human rights.\",\"translation\":\"Las leyes deben proteger la dignidad y los derechos humanos fundamentales.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:06:59\"},{\"content\":\"Power without ethics becomes oppression and corruption.\",\"translation\":\"El poder sin \\u00e9tica se convierte en opresi\\u00f3n y corrupci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:07:03\"},{\"content\":\"Ethical politics balances freedom, equality, and social responsibility.\",\"translation\":\"La pol\\u00edtica \\u00e9tica equilibra libertad, igualdad y responsabilidad social.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:07:07\"},{\"content\":\"Public decisions must prioritize common good over profit.\",\"translation\":\"Las decisiones p\\u00fablicas deben priorizar el bien com\\u00fan sobre el beneficio.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 14:07:13\"},{\"content\":\"Political ethics guides power toward justice and responsibility.\",\"translation\":\"La \\u00e9tica pol\\u00edtica orienta el poder hacia la justicia y la responsabilidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:03:56\"},{\"content\":\"Accountability strengthens trust between citizens and institutions.\",\"translation\":\"La rendici\\u00f3n de cuentas refuerza la confianza entre los ciudadanos y las instituciones.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:29\"},{\"content\":\"Dialogue and tolerance prevent violence and polarization.\",\"translation\":\"El di\\u00e1logo y la tolerancia previenen la violencia y la polarizaci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:35\"},{\"content\":\"Justice demands fair processes and equal opportunities.\",\"translation\":\"La justicia exige procesos equitativos e igualdad de oportunidades.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:39\"},{\"content\":\"Ethical leaders accept limits, criticism, and legal control.\",\"translation\":\"Los l\\u00edderes \\u00e9ticos aceptan los l\\u00edmites, las cr\\u00edticas y el control legal.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:43\"},{\"content\":\"Political participation requires informed, critical, and active citizens.\",\"translation\":\"La participaci\\u00f3n pol\\u00edtica requiere ciudadanos informados, cr\\u00edticos y activos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:48\"},{\"content\":\"Ethics reminds politics of its human purpose.\",\"translation\":\"La \\u00e9tica recuerda a la pol\\u00edtica su finalidad humana.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:54\"},{\"content\":\"Without ethics, democracy weakens and public trust collapses.\",\"translation\":\"Sin \\u00e9tica, la democracia se debilita y la confianza de los ciudadanos se derrumba.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:04:58\"},{\"content\":\"Ethical politics seeks peace, inclusion, and sustainable development.\",\"translation\":\"La pol\\u00edtica \\u00e9tica busca la paz, la inclusi\\u00f3n y el desarrollo sostenible.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:05:03\"},{\"content\":\"Education strengthens ethical judgment within political communities.\",\"translation\":\"La educaci\\u00f3n refuerza el juicio \\u00e9tico en las comunidades pol\\u00edticas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:05:08\"},{\"content\":\"Solidarity connects individual interests with collective wellbeing.\",\"translation\":\"La solidaridad conecta los intereses individuales con el bienestar colectivo.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:05:20\"},{\"content\":\"Media responsibility supports truth and democratic accountability.\",\"translation\":\"La responsabilidad de los medios de comunicaci\\u00f3n apoya la verdad y la responsabilidad democr\\u00e1tica.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:05:20\"},{\"content\":\"Ethical compromise differs from betrayal of core principles.\",\"translation\":\"El compromiso \\u00e9tico difiere de la traici\\u00f3n a los principios fundamentales.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:05:25\"},{\"content\":\"Political ethics evolves through culture, history, and reflection.\",\"translation\":\"La \\u00e9tica pol\\u00edtica evoluciona a trav\\u00e9s de la cultura, la historia y la reflexi\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 19:05:34\"}]', 0, NULL, '2025-12-18 13:06:31'),
(182, 23, 'Good customer service', 'Buen servicio al cliente', 'Good customer service is very important. When a client calls or writes to you, you should be polite and clear. First, listen carefully to what the client says. Do not interrupt. Show that you understand. You can say, “I see,” or “I understand your problem.”\r\n\r\nNext, speak slowly and use simple words. This helps the client feel comfortable. If you do not know the answer, do not worry. Tell the client, “I will check it and get back to you.” It is better to be honest than to give wrong information.\r\n\r\nAlways be friendly. Use phrases like “How can I help you?” or “Thank you for your message.” When a client is angry, stay calm. Try to find a solution. You can say, “Let me see what I can do for you.”', '[{\"content\":\"Good customer service is very important.\",\"translation\":\"Un buen servicio al cliente es muy importante.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 16:45:11\"},{\"content\":\"When a client calls or writes to you, you should be polite and clear.\",\"translation\":\"Cuando un cliente te llama o te escribe, debes ser educado y claro.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:10:49\"},{\"content\":\"First, listen carefully to what the client says.\",\"translation\":\"En primer lugar, hay que escuchar atentamente lo que dice el cliente.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:10:54\"},{\"content\":\"Do not interrupt.\",\"translation\":\"No interrumpa.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:10:58\"},{\"content\":\"Show that you understand.\",\"translation\":\"Demuestra que lo entiendes.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:00\"},{\"content\":\"You can say, \\u201cI see,\\u201d or \\u201cI understand your problem.\\u201d\",\"translation\":\"Puedes decir: \\\"Ya veo\\\" o \\\"Entiendo tu problema\\\".\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:02\"},{\"content\":\"Next, speak slowly and use simple words.\",\"translation\":\"A continuaci\\u00f3n, hable despacio y utilice palabras sencillas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:07\"},{\"content\":\"This helps the client feel comfortable.\",\"translation\":\"Esto ayuda al cliente a sentirse c\\u00f3modo.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:11\"},{\"content\":\"If you do not know the answer, do not worry.\",\"translation\":\"Si no sabe la respuesta, no se preocupe.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:14\"},{\"content\":\"Tell the client, \\u201cI will check it and get back to you.\\u201d It is better to be honest than to give wrong information.\",\"translation\":\"D\\u00edgale al cliente: \\\"Lo comprobar\\u00e9 y le informar\\u00e9\\\". Es mejor ser sincero que dar informaci\\u00f3n err\\u00f3nea.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:17\"},{\"content\":\"Always be friendly.\",\"translation\":\"S\\u00e9 siempre amable.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:25\"},{\"content\":\"Use phrases like \\u201cHow can I help you?\\u201d or \\u201cThank you for your message.\\u201d When a client is angry, stay calm.\",\"translation\":\"Utilice frases como \\\"\\u00bfEn qu\\u00e9 puedo ayudarle?\\\" o \\\"Gracias por su mensaje\\\". Cuando un cliente est\\u00e9 enfadado, mantenga la calma.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:26\"},{\"content\":\"Try to find a solution.\",\"translation\":\"Intenta encontrar una soluci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:40\"},{\"content\":\"You can say, \\u201cLet me see what I can do for you.\\u201d\",\"translation\":\"Puedes decir: \\\"D\\u00e9jame ver qu\\u00e9 puedo hacer por ti\\\".\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-18 20:11:43\"}]', 0, NULL, '2025-12-18 15:44:56'),
(187, 23, 'She prefers to', 'Prefiere', 'She prefers to read. She reads in the morning, in the afternoon and at night.\r\n\r\nI give all of the vegetables to mom and dad. They like to cook in our small kitchen. I eat any vegetable but my sister eats only a few.\r\n\r\nMy family always eats breakfast and dinner together. We talk. We laugh. Then my sister washes the dishes.\r\n\r\nAt night dad likes to listen to music. Mom works on the computer. I watch television. And my sister reads.', '[{\"content\":\"She prefers to read.\",\"translation\":\"Prefiere leer.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:16\"},{\"content\":\"She reads in the morning, in the afternoon and at night.\",\"translation\":\"Lee por la ma\\u00f1ana, por la tarde y por la noche.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:19\"},{\"content\":\"I give all of the vegetables to mom and dad.\",\"translation\":\"Doy todas las verduras a mam\\u00e1 y pap\\u00e1.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:25\"},{\"content\":\"They like to cook in our small kitchen.\",\"translation\":\"Les gusta cocinar en nuestra peque\\u00f1a cocina.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:29\"},{\"content\":\"I eat any vegetable but my sister eats only a few.\",\"translation\":\"Yo como cualquier verdura, pero mi hermana s\\u00f3lo come unas pocas.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:33\"},{\"content\":\"My family always eats breakfast and dinner together.\",\"translation\":\"Mi familia siempre desayuna y cena junta.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:38\"},{\"content\":\"We talk.\",\"translation\":\"Hablamos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:43\"},{\"content\":\"We laugh.\",\"translation\":\"Nos re\\u00edmos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:45\"},{\"content\":\"Then my sister washes the dishes.\",\"translation\":\"Luego mi hermana lava los platos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:46\"},{\"content\":\"At night dad likes to listen to music.\",\"translation\":\"Por la noche, a pap\\u00e1 le gusta escuchar m\\u00fasica.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:50\"},{\"content\":\"Mom works on the computer.\",\"translation\":\"Mam\\u00e1 trabaja en el ordenador.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:54\"},{\"content\":\"I watch television.\",\"translation\":\"Veo la televisi\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:57\"},{\"content\":\"And my sister reads.\",\"translation\":\"Y mi hermana lee.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-19 19:27:59\"}]', 0, NULL, '2025-12-18 17:54:46'),
