(190, 61, 'My name is', 'Me llamo', 'My name is Ahmed. I am a student. I live with my family in a small house. I like my life because it is simple and calm. Every day I wake up at six o’clock in the morning. I brush my teeth and wash my face. Then I eat breakfast with my family. I usually eat bread, cheese, and drink tea.\r\n\r\nAfter that, I go to the university. I study engineering. I like my subjects, but sometimes they are difficult. I listen to the teacher and take notes in my notebook. I try to understand the lesson well.', '[{\"content\":\"My name is Ahmed.\",\"translation\":\"Me llamo Ahmed.\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-12-21 21:28:26\"}]', 0, NULL, '2025-12-21 20:28:17'),
