(192, 111, 'Learning English can', 'Aprender inglés puede', 'Learning English can be simple and enjoyable for everyone.\r\nReading short texts helps improve vocabulary and understanding.\r\nPractice every day, even if you only read a little.\r\nMistakes are normal and part of the learning process.\r\nFocus on meaning, not perfection.\r\nStories make learning more interesting and memorable.\r\nSimple sentences build confidence quickly.\r\nConsistency is more important than speed.\r\nReading aloud improves pronunciation and fluency.\r\nNew words become familiar through repetition.\r\nEnjoy the process and stay motivated.\r\nEnglish opens doors to new opportunities.', '[{\"content\":\"Learning English can be simple and enjoyable for everyone.\",\"translation\":\"Aprender ingl\\u00e9s puede ser sencillo y divertido para todos.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:12\"},{\"content\":\"Reading short texts helps improve vocabulary and understanding.\",\"translation\":\"Leer textos cortos ayuda a mejorar el vocabulario y la comprensi\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:17\"},{\"content\":\"Practice every day, even if you only read a little.\",\"translation\":\"Practica todos los d\\u00edas, aunque solo leas un poco.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:22\"},{\"content\":\"Mistakes are normal and part of the learning process.\",\"translation\":\"Los errores son normales y forman parte del proceso de aprendizaje.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:26\"},{\"content\":\"Focus on meaning, not perfection.\",\"translation\":\"C\\u00e9ntrate en el significado, no en la perfecci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:29\"},{\"content\":\"Stories make learning more interesting and memorable.\",\"translation\":\"Las historias hacen que el aprendizaje sea m\\u00e1s interesante y memorable.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:33\"},{\"content\":\"Simple sentences build confidence quickly.\",\"translation\":\"Las oraciones simples generan confianza r\\u00e1pidamente.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:36\"},{\"content\":\"Consistency is more important than speed.\",\"translation\":\"La consistencia es m\\u00e1s importante que la velocidad.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:40\"},{\"content\":\"Reading aloud improves pronunciation and fluency.\",\"translation\":\"Leer en voz alta mejora la pronunciaci\\u00f3n y la fluidez.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:43\"},{\"content\":\"New words become familiar through repetition.\",\"translation\":\"Las palabras nuevas se vuelven familiares con la repetici\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:58:57\"},{\"content\":\"Enjoy the process and stay motivated.\",\"translation\":\"Disfruta del proceso y mant\\u00e9n la motivaci\\u00f3n.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:59:00\"},{\"content\":\"English opens doors to new opportunities.\",\"translation\":\"El ingl\\u00e9s abre las puertas a nuevas oportunidades.\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-01-12 12:59:03\"}]', 0, NULL, '2026-01-12 12:52:24');
